\par \lquote Sure you can manage that broom, Potter?\rquote  said a cold, drawling voice.
\par Draco Malfoy had arrived for a closer look, Crabbe and Goyle right behind him.
\par \lquote Yeah, reckon so,\rquote  said Harry casually.
\par \lquote Got plenty of special features, hasn\rquote t it?\rquote  said Malfoy, eyes glit\-tering maliciously. \lquote Shame it doesn\rquote t come with a parachute \endash  in case you get too near a Dementor.\rquote 
