\par \lquote \endash  he\rquote s a rat \endash \rquote 
\par \lquote \endash  Pettigrew\rquote s front paw, I mean, finger, he cut it off \endash \rquote 
\par \lquote \endash  Pettigrew attacked Ron, it wasn\rquote t Sirius \endash \rquote 
