\par \lquote I am going to lock you in. It is \endash \rquote  he consulted his watch, \lquote five minutes to midnight. Miss Granger, three turns should do it. Good luck.\rquote 
\par \lquote Good luck?\rquote  Harry repeated, as the door closed behind Dumbledore. \lquote Three turns? What\rquote s he talking about? What are we supposed to do?\rquote 
